page.title: 10James and Lee's weekend
page.content: {Lee's Weekend I wake up at 8am and have some Grapefruit juice and some cornflakes with coffee.I put the television on and watch W.A.C. the Wide awake club.I go to football for cubs until 12.00 o'clock.After dinner I play at the Villge Hall for an hour then I go home to get an ice cream then watch the football on television. {James' Weekend. ' I get up at about 10 o' clock and have some breakfast, a boiled egg, frosties and some toast. Then I get washed and dressed then I probably go out somewhere or perhaps watch some TV. Later I will have my lunch and I may play a game of snooker with my dad. I may listen to some Breakdance music or some electro music,then I watch more TV then I go to bed.
